<div class="hero">
  <div class="breadcrumb" style="font-size:.8rem;color:var(--ink3);margin-bottom:16px;">
    <a href="index.html" style="color:var(--ink3);text-decoration:none;">Home</a> › Healthy BMI by Age
  </div>
  <h1>Healthy BMI by Age<br><em>Men & Women, 20–65+</em></h1>
  <p>The standard BMI range (18.5–24.9) applies to all adults — but average BMI, body composition, and health risks shift significantly with age. Here's what the evidence shows for every decade.</p>
</div>

<div class="container">

  <!-- Byline / E-E-A-T -->
  <div style="font-size:.8rem;color:var(--ink3);margin-bottom:24px;padding-bottom:16px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);">
